data.name: label2.Text
data.value: This list view shows what is possible. It shows: customTile view; alternate line colouring; super-doopers grouping (trying grouping on 'Cooking Skill' column); dynamic tool tips for cells (hold down Control key to see); full drag and drop handling (drop someone on some else to "marry" them); hyperlinks (all occupations are hyperlinks, except those starting with "s").
